<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4407172>
        a                        fabio:Figure ;
        dc:description           "FIGURE 9. Caryocorbula swiftiana (C. B. Adams, 1852). A–H. Specimens in pre-accretion stage. A–D. CIB 1165. A. external view of left valve. B. internal view of left valve. C. external view of right valve. D. internal view of right valve. E–F. CIB 1162. E. external view of left valve. F. external view of right valve. G–H. CIB 1074. G. external view of left valve. H. external view of right valve. I–L. Hinge of shells with different thickening. I. CIB 1165, left valve hinge of specimen pre-accretion stage. J. CMPHRM 2396, left valve hinge of specimen in post-accretion stage. K. CIB 1165, right valve hinge of specimen in pre-accretion stage. L. CMPHRM 2396, right valve hinge of specimen in post-accretion stage. Scale bars: A–F= 2mm; G–L= 1mm. Legends: c= chondrophore. cs= cardinal socket. ct= cardinal tooth; k= knob; rs= resilial socket." ;
        fabio:hasRepresentation  "https://zenodo.org/record/4407172/files/figure.png" .

